<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-773" src="images/dxglcfg-affinity.png" alt="" width="521" height="191" /></p>
<p>Overrides the core affinity of the program. This can be useful to diagnose performance or stability issues.</p>
<p>For DXGL versions below 0.6.0 enabling single core may improve performance.</p>